329
00:16:25,302 --> 00:16:28,321
Preocupa-se com a Pied Piper?

330
00:16:28,496 --> 00:16:30,636
Se me preocupo com a Pied Piper?

331
00:16:30,666 --> 00:16:33,921
- É claro...
